https://pgexercises.com/ (PostgreSQL Excercises) (English) -> Plattform, where you can solve some PSQL excercises (several categories from basic to recursive) 

https://sql-island.informatik.uni-kl.de/ (SQL Island) (German, English, Portugese, Hungarian) -> interesting game, 
  that you can control with sql commands, created by German technical university Kaiserslautern.
  POV in the game: the main charakter landed on an island and you need to help him to solve several challenges - with the help of sql commands.
(language can be changed at the hamburger button)
